# Abstract

This document defines the top-level Transaction CrossMail (TXXM) envelope used
by Kapnet. The TXXM envelope is the canonical transport and replay unit for
Kapnet-native actions. It includes addressing, object class, payload
commitment, dependency references, validity horizon, postage hooks, signatures,
and settlement hints.

